      <div class="page-header-area">
        <h1 class="page-title">Avatar</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">
          The Avatar is a compact visual representation of a user or entity. It displays a profile photo, user initials, or a generic placeholder icon when no personal image is available.
        </p>
        <nav class="content-tabs">
          <button class="tab-item active">Overview</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Style</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Usage</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Code</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Accessibility</button>
        </nav>
      </div>
      <div class="main-content-area">
        <div class="main-content-inner">

        <!-- ═══ OVERVIEW TAB ═══ -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-overview">

        <!-- Anatomy Section -->
        <h3 id="anatomy" class="doc-h3">Anatomy</h3>
        <style>
          .anatomy-diagram { background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 48px 40px; margin-bottom: 28px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
          [data-theme="light"] .anatomy-diagram { background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.07); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05); }
          .anatomy-diagram::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2563eb, #60a5fa, #06b6d4); }
          .anat-marker-inline { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #3b82f6); color: #fff !important; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35); }
          .anat-legend { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
          .anat-legend-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; padding: 20px; background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 14px; transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1); }
          [data-theme="light"] .anat-legend-item { background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.07); box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.04); }
          .anat-legend-item strong { display: block; font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--prism-text); margin-bottom: 6px; }
          .anat-legend-item span { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--prism-text-muted); }
        </style>

        <div class="anatomy-diagram">
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 40px 0;">
            <div style="position: relative; width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px dashed rgba(37,99,235,0.4); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2); overflow: visible;">
              <!-- Container marker -->
              <div style="position: absolute; top: -36px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">
                <span class="anat-marker-inline">1</span><div style="width: 2px; height: 16px; background: #2563eb;"></div>
              </div>
              <!-- Content marker -->
              <div style="position: absolute; bottom: -36px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); display: flex; flex-direction: column-reverse; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">
                <span class="anat-marker-inline">2</span><div style="width: 2px; height: 16px; background: #2563eb;"></div>
              </div>
              <!-- Inner content: initials -->
              <span style="color: #fff; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -1px;">JD</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="anat-legend">
          <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">1</span><div><strong>Container</strong><span>Circular frame that clips content. Size determines the diameter.</span></div></div>
          <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">2</span><div><strong>Content</strong><span>Image (profile photo), Initials (1-2 chars on tinted bg), or Placeholder Icon (generic person silhouette).</span></div></div>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <!-- Live demo -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: 64px;">
          <h2 id="live-demo" class="doc-section-title" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Preview</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">Explore the avatar types and sizes. Hover over the Hover type to see the editable overlay.</p>

          <style>
            .demo-container { border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
            .demo-toolbar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px 20px; background: var(--prism-surface); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--prism-border); }
            [data-theme="light"] .demo-container { border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.14); box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08); }
            [data-theme="light"] .demo-toolbar { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.06); }
            .demo-toolbar-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
            .demo-theme-pill { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; background: rgba(37,99,235,0.08); color: var(--prism-violet); border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.2); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s ease; }
            .demo-theme-pill:hover { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.14); }
            .demo-theme-pill svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }
            .demo-canvas { padding: 64px; position: relative; background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 24px 24px; background-color: #0a0a0c66; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 280px; gap: 32px; transition: background-color 0.5s ease; }
            [data-theme="light"] .demo-canvas { background-color: #f4f6fb; background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px); }

            /* Avatar demo styles */
            .avatar-demo {
              border-radius: 50%; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative; flex-shrink: 0;
              font-family: 'Zoho Puvi', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.2s ease;
            }
            .avatar-sm { width: 32px; height: 32px; font-size: 12px; }
            .avatar-md { width: 48px; height: 48px; font-size: 16px; }
            .avatar-lg { width: 72px; height: 72px; font-size: 24px; }

            .avatar-image { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2); }
            .avatar-initials { background: #EAF0FC; color: #0E2553; }
            .avatar-placeholder { background: #F0F2F5; color: #8893AD; }
            .avatar-hover { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2); cursor: pointer; }
            .avatar-hover .avatar-overlay {
              position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
              background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
              opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
            }
            .avatar-hover:hover .avatar-overlay { opacity: 1; }
            .avatar-disabled { opacity: 0.4; pointer-events: none; }

            html:not([data-theme="light"]) .avatar-initials { background: rgba(234, 240, 252, 0.12); color: #c4d5f0; }
            html:not([data-theme="light"]) .avatar-placeholder { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }

            .demo-avatar-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
            .demo-avatar-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--prism-text-muted); min-width: 60px; text-align: right; }
          </style>

          <div class="demo-container">
            <div class="demo-canvas">
              <!-- Row 1: Large -->
              <div class="demo-avatar-row">
                <span class="demo-avatar-label">Large</span>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-lg avatar-image" title="Image"></div>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-lg avatar-initials" title="Initials">JD</div>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-lg avatar-placeholder" title="Placeholder">
                  <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 12c2.7 0 4.8-2.1 4.8-4.8S14.7 2.4 12 2.4 7.2 4.5 7.2 7.2 9.3 12 12 12zm0 2.4c-3.2 0-9.6 1.6-9.6 4.8v2.4h19.2v-2.4c0-3.2-6.4-4.8-9.6-4.8z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-lg avatar-hover" title="Hover (editable)">
                  <div class="avatar-overlay">
                    <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2z"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4"/></svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Row 2: Medium -->
              <div class="demo-avatar-row">
                <span class="demo-avatar-label">Medium</span>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-md avatar-image" title="Image"></div>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-md avatar-initials" title="Initials">AB</div>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-md avatar-placeholder" title="Placeholder">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 12c2.7 0 4.8-2.1 4.8-4.8S14.7 2.4 12 2.4 7.2 4.5 7.2 7.2 9.3 12 12 12zm0 2.4c-3.2 0-9.6 1.6-9.6 4.8v2.4h19.2v-2.4c0-3.2-6.4-4.8-9.6-4.8z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-md avatar-hover" title="Hover (editable)">
                  <div class="avatar-overlay">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M23 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 012 2z"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4"/></svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Row 3: Small -->
              <div class="demo-avatar-row">
                <span class="demo-avatar-label">Small</span>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-sm avatar-image" title="Image"></div>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-sm avatar-initials" title="Initials">K</div>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-sm avatar-placeholder" title="Placeholder">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 12c2.7 0 4.8-2.1 4.8-4.8S14.7 2.4 12 2.4 7.2 4.5 7.2 7.2 9.3 12 12 12zm0 2.4c-3.2 0-9.6 1.6-9.6 4.8v2.4h19.2v-2.4c0-3.2-6.4-4.8-9.6-4.8z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="avatar-demo avatar-sm avatar-image avatar-disabled" title="Disabled"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="doc-section">
          <h3 id="content-guidelines" class="doc-h3">Content Guidelines<span class="h3-badge" style="background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1); color: var(--prism-violet);">Recommended</span></h3>
          <div class="do-dont-grid">
            <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding: 0;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;">Always provide accessible text alternative (alt or aria-label).</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;">Use Image type when profile photo is available.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;">Fall back gracefully: Image &rarr; Initials &rarr; Placeholder Icon.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;">Use consistent avatar sizes within same context.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding: 0;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;">Don't use Hover type as default or in read-only views.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;">Don't use initials with more than 2 characters.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;">Don't stretch or deform images.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;">Don't use avatars as sole identification in critical contexts.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div> <!-- End tab-overview -->

      <!-- ═══ STYLE TAB ═══ -->
      <div class="tab-content" id="tab-style" style="display: none; padding-top: 32px;">
        <h2 id="style-overview" class="doc-section-title">Style</h2>
        <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens, visual axes, and specifications that define the Avatar's visual language.</p>

        <style>
          .size-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; }
          .size-table th { text-align: left; padding: 14px 12px; color: var(--prism-text-muted); font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--prism-border); }
          .size-table td { padding: 16px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--prism-border); color: var(--prism-text); vertical-align: middle; }
          .size-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.02); }
          .size-table code { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 12.5px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(37,99,235,0.06); color: var(--prism-violet); }
          .state-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 14px; margin-top: 24px; }
          .state-card { padding: 24px 16px; border-radius: 14px; background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); text-align: center; transition: all 0.25s ease; }
          [data-theme="light"] .state-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.07); box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(37,99,235,0.04); }
          .state-card:hover { border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.3); transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(37,99,235,0.08); }
          .state-card-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--prism-text); margin-top: 16px; }
          .state-card-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--prism-text-muted); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.5; }
        </style>

        <!-- Variant Axes -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="variant-axes" class="doc-section-title">Variant Axes</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">The Avatar component is defined across three independent axes that combine to produce all possible permutations.</p>

          <table class="size-table">
            <thead>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--prism-border);">
                <th>Axis</th>
                <th>Values</th>
                <th>Description</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><strong>Size</strong></td><td>Small, Medium, Large</td><td>Diameter of avatar circle</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Type</strong></td><td>Image, Initials, Placeholder Icon, Hover</td><td>Content displayed inside</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>State</strong></td><td>Default, Disabled</td><td>Interaction state</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <p style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--prism-text-muted);">Total: 3 &times; 4 &times; 2 = <strong>24 variants</strong></p>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <!-- Types -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="types" class="doc-section-title">Types</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Each avatar type serves a specific content scenario, from photo display to anonymous placeholders.</p>

          <table class="size-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Type</th><th>When to Use</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><strong>Image</strong></td><td>User has uploaded a profile photo.</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Initials</strong></td><td>No photo available, but the user's name is known.</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Placeholder Icon</strong></td><td>No photo or name available.</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Hover</strong></td><td>Editable avatar surface (e.g., profile settings).</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <div style="margin-top: 24px; padding: 16px 20px; background: rgba(37,99,235,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.15); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start;">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 16v-4"></path><path d="M12 8h.01"></path></svg>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--prism-text); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"><strong>Fallback Chain:</strong> Image &rarr; Initials &rarr; Placeholder Icon. Always attempt to show the most personalized representation first.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <!-- Sizes -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="sizes" class="doc-section-title">Sizes</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Three sizes to fit different layout contexts. All sizes share pill (9999px) border radius for a perfect circle.</p>

          <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 32px; justify-content: center; margin: 32px 0; padding: 40px; background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 16px;">
            <div style="text-align: center;">
              <div class="avatar-demo avatar-sm avatar-initials" style="margin: 0 auto;">S</div>
              <div style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--prism-text-muted); margin-top: 12px; font-weight: 600;">Small (32px)</div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
              <div class="avatar-demo avatar-md avatar-initials" style="margin: 0 auto;">M</div>
              <div style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--prism-text-muted); margin-top: 12px; font-weight: 600;">Medium (48px)</div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
              <div class="avatar-demo avatar-lg avatar-initials" style="margin: 0 auto;">L</div>
              <div style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--prism-text-muted); margin-top: 12px; font-weight: 600;">Large (72px)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <!-- States -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="states" class="doc-section-title">States</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Avatars support two interaction states to communicate availability and interactivity.</p>
          <div class="state-grid">
            <div class="state-card">
              <div class="avatar-demo avatar-md avatar-image" style="margin: 0 auto;"></div>
              <div class="state-card-title">Default</div>
              <div class="state-card-desc">Standard resting state, fully opaque</div>
            </div>
            <div class="state-card">
              <div class="avatar-demo avatar-md avatar-image avatar-disabled" style="margin: 0 auto;"></div>
              <div class="state-card-title">Disabled</div>
              <div class="state-card-desc">Opacity 0.4, no interaction</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <!-- Design Tokens -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h3 id="design-tokens" class="doc-h3">Design Tokens Used<span class="h3-badge" style="background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1); color: var(--prism-violet);">Tokens</span></h3>
          <table class="size-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Token</th><th>Usage</th><th>Value</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><code>BG-Tertiary</code></td><td>Placeholder background</td><td>#F0F2F5</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>BG-Accent-Secondary</code></td><td>Initials tinted background</td><td>#EAF0FC</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Text-Primary</code></td><td>Initials text color</td><td>#0E2553</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Icon-Subtle</code></td><td>Placeholder icon color</td><td>#8893AD</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Border-Accent-Focus</code></td><td>Focus ring for editable avatars</td><td>#006AFF</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Overlay/Black-50</code></td><td>Hover overlay background</td><td>rgba(0,0,0,0.5)</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>radius-pill</code></td><td>Circular shape</td><td>9999px</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ═══ USAGE TAB ═══ -->
      <div class="tab-content" id="tab-usage" style="display: none; padding-top: 32px;">

        <!-- When and Where to Use Section -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="when-to-use" class="doc-section-title">When and Where to Use</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Avatars visually represent users and entities across the interface, providing quick identification in lists, headers, and interactive contexts.</p>

          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; margin-top: 24px;">
            <div style="padding: 24px; background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 12px; transition: all 0.25s ease;">
              <h3 id="when-to-use-details" style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--prism-text); margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                When to use
              </h3>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 14.5px;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">Navigation headers for logged-in user identification.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">User lists and team member displays.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">Comment threads and activity feeds.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent;">Profile pages and user detail panels.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 24px; background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 12px; transition: all 0.25s ease;">
              <h3 id="when-not-to-use" style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--prism-text); margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#e42527" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
                When NOT to use
              </h3>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 14.5px;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">As decorative elements without user association.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">As buttons or action triggers (except Hover type for photo upload).</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">For non-person entities where a logo or icon is more appropriate.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent;">In contexts where the user's full name is sufficient.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <!-- Initials Generation -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="initials-generation" class="doc-section-title">Initials Generation</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Rules for extracting initials from user names to display inside the avatar.</p>
          <table class="size-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Name Format</th><th>Initials</th><th>Rule</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>"Jane Doe"</td><td><strong>JD</strong></td><td>First letter of first and last name</td></tr>
              <tr><td>"Javier"</td><td><strong>J</strong></td><td>First letter of single name</td></tr>
              <tr><td>"Jane Marie Doe"</td><td><strong>JD</strong></td><td>First letter of first and last name (skip middle)</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Unknown / empty</td><td><em>Placeholder Icon</em></td><td>Fall back to generic person silhouette</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <!-- Detailed Do's and Don'ts -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="detailed-guidelines" class="doc-section-title">Complete Do's and Don'ts</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Visual and interaction guidelines to ensure avatars are effective, consistent, and accessible.</p>
          <div class="do-dont-grid">
            <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding: 0;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Provide alt text:</strong> Always include alt or aria-label with the user's full name for image avatars.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Use fallback chain:</strong> Attempt Image first, then Initials, then Placeholder Icon for graceful degradation.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Keep sizes consistent:</strong> Use the same avatar size within lists, tables, and repeated UI contexts.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Pair with name:</strong> In most contexts, display the user's name alongside the avatar for clarity.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding: 0;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>No long initials:</strong> Don't use more than 2 characters for initials.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>No deformed images:</strong> Don't stretch, squish, or crop images in non-uniform ways.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>No misused Hover type:</strong> Don't show the Hover overlay in read-only or non-editable contexts.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>No sole identification:</strong> Don't use avatars as the only way to identify users in critical workflows.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <!-- Related -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="related" class="doc-section-title">Related</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Components that complement or can be used alongside the Avatar.</p>
          <div class="related-grid">
            <a href="#" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="9" cy="12" r="4"/><circle cx="15" cy="12" r="4"/></svg> Avatar Group</a>
            <a href="Badges.html" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l2 2"/></svg> Badge</a>
            <a href="Cards.html" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="3"/><path d="M3 10h18"/></svg> User Card / Profile Card</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <!-- References -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="references" class="doc-section-title">References</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens and resources for implementing the Avatar component.</p>
          <ul class="doc-list">
            <li><strong>Figma Node:</strong> <code style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(37,99,235,0.06); color: var(--prism-violet);">16021:26134</code> — Component Set: Avatar</li>
