        <div class="doc-section">
          <h3 id="instance-overrides" class="doc-h3">Instance Overrides</h3>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Customizations available when placing an Avatar instance in your design.</p>
          <ol class="doc-list">
            <li><strong>Image Source:</strong> Swap the placeholder gradient with an actual user profile photo URL or asset.</li>
            <li><strong>Initials Text:</strong> Override the default initials with the target user's computed initials (1-2 characters).</li>
            <li><strong>Overlay Icon:</strong> For Hover type, optionally swap the camera icon for a pencil/edit icon depending on context.</li>
            <li><strong>Background Color:</strong> Initials type background tint can be overridden per user or team color assignment.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
